{"tid":461542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲足協搞歐洲聯賽不得止,重想搞全球聯賽","createTime":"2017-11-07T16:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:30:42.000Z","uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c61ed54fd0947dafa07c5ffe5a88b06ee4de6ef3","tid":461542,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41871546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F41871546&d=%2B8t1zD76Akrb5gSLLcVgAo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=beeef005\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F41871546&h=da8cab98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/41871546</a><br />\n<br />\nUefa says it has &quot;initiated&quot; talks with Fifa and other regional confederations about expanding its new Nations League into a global competition.<br />\n<br />\nThe Nations League starts next September and will replace most international friendlies on Fifa's calendar which involve European teams.<br />\n<br />\nUefa and Fifa told BBC Sport they are having &quot;constructive discussions&quot; about the league's development.<br />\n<br />\nBut Uefa says &quot;no decisions have been made&quot;."},{"pid":"631285b4581a597c3bc2537f33c12e8d64e4f20e","tid":461542,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:37:45.000Z","msg":"到時d大球會年年踢70場波不是夢"},{"pid":"3fd4d0ed24db6e0f8f19314b9eb6d8218fab0535","tid":461542,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時d大球會年年踢70場波不是夢</blockquote><br />\n越有錢越有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8002adc5993d2a706c3b82bcba78de79f1b8dd0","tid":461542,"uid":53726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到時d大球會年年踢70場波不是夢</blockquote><br />\n越有錢越有得玩<img src=\"/asset